marketing:
Shell Rotella MP Grease is designed for multipurpose grease lubrication of on and off-road vehicles and equipment for general chassis, springs, pivot points, low speed bearings (not disk brake wheel bearings), and
ancillary equipment such as mowers, trailers, lifts, loader buckets, etc.
